# UI Test Conventions

When writing or editing UI tests, follow these patterns:

## Query Priority
- Prefer `getByRole`, `getByLabelText` over `getByText` or `getByTestId`
- Use `findBy*` for async elements; `waitFor` for custom assertions

## Router
- Wrap route-dependent components in `createMemoryRouter` + `RouterProvider` or `MemoryRouter`

## API Mocking
- Use MSW handlers in `mocks/handlers.ts`; start server in `setup.ts`

## shadcn
- Test accessible behavior (roles, labels); avoid asserting internal DOM structure
